      <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Always perform maintenance and preventive maintenance
according to specifications to ensure reliable operation.</note>
      <note class="- topic/note ">Always record and document the performed maintenance. This is
important to identify adjustments to the maintenance and replacement
schedules according to the specific system and environment.</note>
      <section platform="PxW SDC" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">General Battery Maintenance Information</title>
         <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">All recommendations and instructions for battery
maintenance are only for batteries that are supplied by Reality. Reality
does not accept any responsibility for batteries that are not supplied
by Reality.</note>
         <p class="- topic/p ">During operation the battery capacity and the lifetime
are affected by for example:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Corrosion</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Grid growth</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Ripple effects</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Sulphation</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Passivation</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Short circuit</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">None or excessive cycling</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Deep discharge</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Wrong battery room temperature</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Operation with low electrolyte</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Gradual changes in active material</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Normal aging</p>
               </li>
            </ul>It is important consider the previous and current status of the
batteries for accurate preventive maintenance. For more details see
the documentation from the battery manufacturer.</p>
      </section>
