         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The preventive maintenance for the system under normal conditions
consists of:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <xref href="Monthly_Check_CPT_0000327541.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref ">A monthly check</xref>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <xref href="Semi-Annual_Check_CPT_0000327540.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref ">A semi-annual check</xref>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <xref href="Annual_Check_CPT_0000327539.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref ">An annual check</xref>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ul>Depending on the environment and condition of the system it can
be recommended to perform checks more frequently. Reality provides several
service offers to make your maintenance easier, for more information
see <xref href="Customer_Service_Offers_Summary_CPT_0000387701.dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="concept"
                     class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
         </sectiondiv>
